First Aired: 10/24/2008 on Cartoon Network-HD channel
on DirecTv HDTV Digital Satellite 
16:9 widescreen 624 x 352 resolution

This is The Clone Wars episode 5 on the Cartoon Network HDTV channel.


This SDH release is a Proper release to replace the original S1E05 that had flaws in the audio. This release has had the Audio taken from the 3rd Cartoon Network HD broadcast showing on Sunday night that did not have the audio flaws present and the video from the original Friday night Cartoon Network HD broadcast and have been edited together to make this Proper Release.
